<br>
HP<br>
===<br>
Unfocused the 20 pet heal does 32% - focused it does 25%. <br>
So, the focussed 29 fire pet has ~30% more hp than the unfocused.<br>
<br>
Offence<br>
======<br>
To test this I ran to Katta to have the pet hit the banker. I then ran 6 tests each of 10 mins.<br>
<br>
1. Unfocused, no BO, no weapons<br>
- 1381 dmg (93 hits, 120 misses)<br>
2. Unfocused, BO2, no weapons<br>
- 2316 dmg (145 hits, 132 misses)<br>
3. Unfocused, BO2, 2 weapons<br>
- 2423 dmg (152 hits, 168 misses)<br>
<br>
4. Focused, no BO, no weapons<br>
- 1236 dmg (99 hits, 117 misses)<br>
5. Focused, BO2, no weapons<br>
- 2240 dmg (132 hits, 147 misses)<br>
6. Focused, BO2, 2 weapons<br>
- 2189 dmg (140 hits, 153 misses)<br>
<br>
So, much to my surprise the focused pet didnt do more damage - if anything it did less damage. I realize these tests are too short to be conclusive but the data still surprise me.<br>
<br>
Level/Defence:<br>
===========<br>
I havent tested those (yet).<br>
<br>
<br>
Anyway, maybe the focus item only raises hp and not anything else? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tangting>TangTing</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 130<br> <font color=#333333>(10/28/02 2:50:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=778.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Focus items pet damage </span><hr size=1> I wonder how each pet did for spell damage focused versus unfocused. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showPrevMessage?topicID=778.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showNextMessage?topicID=778.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=778.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.threadControl?topicID=778.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=778.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=778.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" va